                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="work_3764">Makhzan al-asrār</title>
                     <title xml:lang="per" key="work_3764">مخزن الاسرار</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Item b. </p>
                        <p>Fragment of the mystical mas̲navī by Niẓāmī. 
</p>
                        <p>Defective at end. 
</p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. 
</p>
                     </note>
